    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――怜の誕生日企画前日　放課後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1999.9999284,
          "startTime": 1.9999999284
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "中等部のみなさん、失礼します\nすず、いるわよね？　一緒に帰るわよ！",
      "startTime": 6.8999999602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっとなんなんですの！？\n教室では静かにしてくださいまし！",
      "startTime": 14.0333332936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "すずの声の方が大きいわよ！\nほら、それより早く帰る準備して",
      "startTime": 19.9000007231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "あと十数時間後には、テーマパークに入るんだから\n忘れ物がないように、しっかり準備を整えないと",
      "startTime": 27.1666673898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "気合いは分かりましたけど、落ち着いてくださいまし\nそんなに焦っても集合時間まで全然余裕が……",
      "startTime": 35.5333340565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "何事も早め早めに動くことが肝心なの",
      "startTime": 39.2666670242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "早めに動くことは大切ですが、さすがに早過ぎますわ！\n怜が楽しみな気持ちは十分伝わりましたから",
      "startTime": 48.7666673898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "……一週間前からずっとカウントダウンしてましたし\n当日のテンションはもっと凄いことになりそうですわね",
      "startTime": 57.4333340565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "何か言った？　喋ってたら三分もロスしちゃったわよ\n芽衣も迎えに行くんだから。ほら、早く",
      "startTime": 69.9000007231,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4439.98884989999,
          "startTime": 74.339989573
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、そんなに急かさないで……\nお待ちなさい、廊下を走ったらダメですわよー！？",
      "startTime": 76.4666668812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "今日明日と二日間の撮影になりますが\nよろしくお願いします！",
      "startTime": 86.833330496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに素敵なホテル、それに料理やケーキも用意して\n下さり、本当にありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 92.5999971627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "良かったですわね、怜\n……さあ、カメラマンさん、準備はよろしいでしょうか",
      "startTime": 98.9666638294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "実は、芽衣達からもお祝いがありまーす！\nいくよ、すずにゃん！　せーのっ……",
      "startTime": 107.5666637579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "お誕生日おめでとう！！",
      "startTime": 111.5423417488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "すず、芽衣！　ありがとう！",
      "startTime": 114.0005729514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "二人で選んだプレゼントもあるんだ\nはい、どーぞ！　開けてみて開けてみてー",
      "startTime": 120.9333314418,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4027.03714350001,
          "startTime": 124.9603685853
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "……これ、テーマパークのマスコットキャラの\nぬいぐるみじゃない！　しかも周年バージョンだわ！",
      "startTime": 129.4603603042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "明日、この子と一緒にテーマパークに行けたら\n怜ちゃん嬉しいだろうなーって思って",
      "startTime": 137.1666688441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、凄く嬉しいわ！\n前の日からこんなに嬉しい誕生日は初めてよ！",
      "startTime": 143.7465126034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、今日の撮影、とっても楽しかったわ……！",
      "startTime": 149.6798582868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "満足そうで良かったですわ\n明日もあるし、そろそろ寝ましょうか",
      "startTime": 158.4131853736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。おやすみ～",
      "startTime": 161.9000103155,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_switch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9751.458660400005,
          "startTime": 171.6514689759
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "明日は、久々のテーマパークなんだし\n悔いが残らないように楽しみたいわね",
      "startTime": 168.1181214011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ～。怜ちゃんが笑顔だと芽衣達も嬉しいよ……",
      "startTime": 172.5181276477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
